{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"11ea95ab8b","title":"配合张学良杨虎城部消灭东来之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e365f71bf","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":19,"articleId":"11ea95ab8b"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1c6eedd4c2","type":"paragraph","text":"配合张学良杨虎城部消灭东来之敌！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"700f2db616","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月19日）周：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"376ac44152","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、时局正在发展，一方面日本军阀、中国汉好、南京右派极力制造内战局面；另一方面西安抗日军、红军、中国人民、中国反蒋实力派、南京左派、国际和平国家，正在结合反对内战，拥护抗。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"15f9a6a5cb","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、苏维埃、共产党十九日主张召集和平会议之通电，乃为团结一切国内、国际左翼及中间势力，为反对内战、拥护抗日而斗争。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"881a013722","type":"paragraph","text":"内、西安抗日军亦应本此共同之总方针而前进丁、坚决消灭进攻之故，为执行此总方针之重要手段戊、红军决向西安集中，配合张杨首先消灭东来之敌","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"f12b6aad25","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"e630ae7d60","type":"paragraph","text":"十九日二十三时","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"},{"id":"c0d092a755","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]西安事变发生后，中共中央应张学良、杨虎城的邀请，派周恩来、博古（秦邦宪）和叶剑英等为代表到西安与张、杨和各界爱国人士共商国是，并同蒋介石直接谈判：同时，在军事上作了以红军主力协同东北军、第十七路军准备迎击“讨逆”军进攻的部署。这是毛泽东给周恩来的电报。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b"}],"page":{"id":"8ecb7bc976","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"11ea95ab8b","start":191,"end":191}}}},"__N_SSG":true}